# Testing Standards

## CRITICAL: This Project Uses Jest, NOT Vitest

### Correct Jest Commands

| Command | Purpose | Duration |
|---------|---------|----------|
| `npm test` | Unit/integration tests | ~10 min |
| `npm run test:all` | ALL tests including performance | ~28 min |
| `npm run test:performance` | Performance tests only | ~20 min |
| `npm test -- <file>` | Specific test file | varies |
| `npm run test:watch` | Watch mode | continuous |
| `npm run test:coverage` | With coverage | ~12 min |

### WRONG Commands (Will Fail)

```bash
# ‚ùå These are Vitest commands - DON'T USE
npm test -- --run
vitest
```

## Test Command Selection

**Regular task completion:** `npm test`

**Parent task completion:**
- Default: `npm test`
- If task modifies release-analysis/release-detection: `npm run test:all`
- If performance-critical: `npm run test:all`

